item.description:
We would like to celebrate our successful first year with all of our members! Come for a gathering around our amazing new stone fire pit, where you can hang out with old friends or make new ones while enjoying the live music of "Hot Sauce", dancing under the stars, and moonlight pontoon boat rides on beautiful Sampson's Pond....Bring friends, spouse, boyfriend, partner, or musical instrument. If you wish, arrive early with a picnic, and enjoy the grounds! BYOB We are excited to see our regular faces as well as new ones

$10.00 per carload so make sure you pack your car full of friends and family!!

Please RSVP by September 25th.
item.name: One Year Celebration!! Campfire Gathering w/ live band & dancing
